version             20160822
revision            1
categories          devel
platforms           darwin
maintainers         ryandesign openmaintainer
license             GPL-3+

description         converts a Subversion repository into one or more Git repositories

long_description    svn2git provides the svn-all-fast-export program which ${description}.

